{"word":"ὑψόθεν","slug":"ὑψόθεν","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑψόθεν</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ὕψος'><el>ὕψος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>from on high, from aloft, from above</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>desuper</el>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>like <el>ὑψοῦ</el>, <i>high, aloft, on high</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>above, over</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}